# SSL Certificate Placeholder
# ============================
# Place your SSL certificates in this directory:
#   - fullchain.pem  (certificate + intermediate CA)
#   - privkey.pem    (private key)
#
# For Let's Encrypt (production):
#   certbot certonly --standalone -d your-domain.com
#   cp /etc/letsencrypt/live/your-domain.com/fullchain.pem ./
#   cp /etc/letsencrypt/live/your-domain.com/privkey.pem ./
#
# Then uncomment the SSL lines in:
#   - docker-compose.yml (port 443)
#   - docker/nginx/nginx.conf (ssl_certificate directives)
